Innovation, inspiration, drive and dedication.




Our Leaders







At First Western, we share an uncommon entrepreneurial edge, possessing diverse backgrounds and impressive credentials. Our ability to think creatively and build a solid plan for execution supports a thriving culture and promotes continued success throughout our organization.
With an innate desire and ability to inspire and motivate others to achieve success, we are dedicated to our clients, our fellow associates, and the ongoing strength and growth of the company.



Executive Team
Our executive team consists of ten leading individuals from across the organization who provide significant experience in wealth management, private banking, financial services, and strategy.






        Scott C. Wylie
      

In 2002 recognizing the need for an integrated approach for delivering financial services to the growing affluent market Scott Wylie co-founded First Western Trust.



    About Scott
  









        Rebecca Cordes
      

Rebecca is executive vice president, support services, First Western Trust, and director of human capital, First Western Financial, Inc.



    About Rebecca
  









        Julie Courkamp
      

Julie joined First Western in September 2006 as controller and earned several promotions. She was promoted to chief financial officer in September of 2013.



    About Julie
  









        Debra Silversmith
      

As Chief Investment Officer, Debbie is responsible for developing First Western’s overall investment strategy and leading the company’s Investment Policy Committee.



    About Debra
  









        Dawn Thompson
      

As Chief Credit Officer, Dawn Thompson is responsible for the asset quality of the organization, including private banking, commercial, and real estate loans.



    About Dawn
  









        Daniel C. Thompson, CFP®
      

Dan is responsible for the overall direction and strategy of the Arizona team and is involved with all aspects of client relationship management.



    About Daniel
  









        Alexis Owen
      

As Director of Brand, Alexis leads the company’s external and internal branding initiatives, including marketing, corporate social responsibility programming, and culture.



    About Alexis
  









        Josh Wilson
      

Josh is responsible for managing the operations and associates of First Western Trust’s regional offices. Josh proactively seeks new business solution opportunities and strengthens relationships with current clients.



    About Josh
  









        Gary Lutz
      

Gary Lutz, commercial banking president, is responsible for growing and leading the company’s teams of subject matter experts.



    About Gary
  









        Tina Ballard
      

Tina Ballard is director of Human Capital.



    About Tina
  






Presidents & Chairmen
Our presidents and chairmen are experts in the private banking, wealth management, and investment management and provide strategic direction for our local offices.






        Trish Stark
      

As President, Trish is responsible for building and strengthening new and existing wealth, investment management, trust, and private banking client relationships.



    About Trish
  









        Charles Bantis
      

As President of our Aspen office, Charles is responsible for the day-to-day operations and business development of the Aspen team.



    About Charles
  









        Jeremy Nicholas
      

As President of the DTC office, Jeremy leads the investment management, private banking, and wealth management teams in delivering tailored solutions to our clients.



    About Jeremy
  









        Matt Gorr
      

As Chairman, Matt is responsible for building and maintaining client relationships in the Boulder community.



    About Matt
  









        Suzanne Johnson
      

Suzanne Johnson, president of First Western Trust’s Denver office, is responsible for building and strengthening new and existing client relationships.



    About Suzanne
  









        Don Silversmith
      

Don Silversmith is chairman of First Western Trust, Cherry Creek, and leads our risk management team where he provides insurance services to high-net-worth individuals.



    About Don
  









        Louis L. Clinton III
      

Lou joined First Western Trust in 2003. As President of the Cherry Creek office, he is responsible for assisting clients with a broad range of financial services.



    About Louis
  









        Timothy A. Morphy
      

Tim is president of First Western Trust, Century City. He joined First Western’s predecessor firm, Ryder Stilwell Investment Advisors in 1995.



    About Timothy
  









         Kay Jones
      

As Chairman, Kay is responsible for growing and maintaining client relationships in wealth planning, investment management, private banking, and trust and estate planning.



    About Kay
  









        Jim Gersack, CFP®
      

As President of the Jackson Hole office, Jim is involved in all aspects of client relationships, wealth and investment management, business development, and the day-to-day operations of the office.



    About Jim
  









        Jim Sprout
      

As Chairman, Jim is responsible for the general leadership of the Northern Colorado office and ensures the overall good of client relationships particularly in the area of wealth management services.



    About Jim
  









        Kristi L. Benningsdorf
      

As President, Kristi is responsible for the day-to-day management and business development of the Northern Colorado.



    About Kristi
  









         Eric Long
      

Eric is responsible for building and strengthening client relationships in commercial and consumer lending, including all aspects of private banking. 



    About Eric
  









        Chad Maze
      

As President of our Phoenix office, Chad is responsible for building and strengthening new and existing wealth, investment management, trust, and private banking client relationships for First Western Trust. 



    About Chad
  






