Denver Office







Denver is the eclectic, energetic hub of business, finance, and entertainment in the Rocky Mountain West. At First Western Trust, you’ll enjoy a spectrum of wealth planning, private banking, and investment management services from a local team active in Denver’s business scene for over 30 years.
Because we’re local, you have immediate access to a team of in-house experts who take the time to understand your financial aspirations and develop a custom-tailored plan to help you reach them. Our Denver team understands the importance of relationships and is committed to providing you with exceptional service, outstanding educational opportunities, and the knowledge and expertise needed to put your financial goals in action.
So a warm welcome from President Suzanne Stratman, and First Western Trust, Denver, the region’s premier private bank and wealth planning company.



Our Colorado Locations
