Capital Markets

Company Overview of First Western Financial, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
First Western Financial, Inc. provides wealth management and private banking institution services for individuals, families, private foundations, and non-profit organizations in the United States. It offers wealth management services in the areas of investment management, philanthropic, retirement consulting, risk management, trust and estate, wealth planning, and market commentary aspects; and private banking services, such as mortgage and treasury management services. The company was incorporated in 2002 and is based in Denver, Colorado with additional offices in Arizona, California, Colorado, and Wyoming.


